  "text": "In Figure 23 , LDOS of zero modes is shown for a varying distance from the wormhole bridge in the units of the radius a of the wormhole center. It was also acquired in the numerical way. For the unperturbed case (0 defects), the resulting plot resembles a line. In [CITATION_1] , the exponential solution is found for this case but with a very slow increase, so, this could be that case. It is also seen from the plot that for the increasing number of the defects, the solution is approaching expressions in Eqs. (54), (55) for the zero modes of the unperturbed wormhole.",
